    "slug": "soc-2-type-1-completed-hot-aisle-secures-initial-compliance-milestone",
    "title": "Hot Aisle Achieves SOC 2 Type 1 Compliance",
    "description": "Hot Aisle has officially completed its SOC 2 Type 1 audit, marking a key milestone in our commitment to security and compliance. This achievement validates the strength of our internal controls and processes for handling customer data. With Type 2 already in motion and expected in three months, we’re on track to meet the highest standards in cloud infrastructure security. Special thanks to Sprinto and ATOM for their guidance and support throughout the process.",
    "contentHtml": "<p><img src=\"/assets/blog/hot-aisle-achieves-soc-2-type-1-compliance/image.png\" alt=\"https://hotaisle.xyz/blog/hot-aisle-achieves-soc-2-type-2-compliance-a-milestone-in-security-and-trust/\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hotaisle.xyz/blog/hot-aisle-achieves-soc-2-type-2-compliance-a-milestone-in-security-and-trust/\">https://hotaisle.xyz/blog/hot-aisle-achieves-soc-2-type-2-compliance-a-milestone-in-security-and-trust/</a></p>\n<h1><strong>Hot Aisle Achieves SOC 2 Type 1 Compliance</strong></h1>\n<p>We’re excited to announce that Hot Aisle has officially completed our SOC 2 Type 1 audit. This marks a major milestone in our journey to build a trusted, secure, and compliant cloud infrastructure platform.</p>\n<p>SOC 2 (System and Organization Controls) is a widely recognized standard developed by the AICPA for evaluating a service provider’s ability to securely manage customer data. The Type 1 audit specifically evaluates the design of our internal controls as of a single point in time.</p>\n<p>For us, this isn’t just a checkbox. It’s proof that we’ve built strong processes from day one, designed to protect our customers’ data, ensure operational integrity, and meet the rigorous standards of enterprise and regulated industries.</p>\n<h3><strong>What’s Next?</strong></h3>\n<p>SOC 2 Type 2 is already underway and on track for completion within the next three months. While Type 1 demonstrates that controls exist, Type 2 validates that those controls are operating effectively over time. We’re confident in our systems and look forward to achieving this next milestone.</p>\n<h3><strong>Special Thanks</strong></h3>\n<p>We couldn’t have done this without the help of our partners:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sprinto</strong> – their compliance automation platform made the process seamless and efficient.</li>\n<li><strong>ATOM</strong> – our audit partner, who worked closely with us to evaluate and document our controls.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re considering SOC 2 compliance and want a referral to a trusted partner, we’re happy to give a referral.</p>\n<p>Hot Aisle is committed to making secure, high-performance compute accessible, without compromise. This is just the beginning.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/blog/hot-aisle-achieves-soc-2-type-1-compliance/image-1.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>",
    "date": "2025-07-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "tags": [
      "Announcements"
    ],
    "author": "Jon Stevens",
    "coverImage": "/assets/blog/soc-2-type-1-completed-hot-aisle-secures-initial-compliance-milestone/header.jpg",
    "metaTitle": "Hot Aisle Completes SOC 2 Type 1 Compliance – Type 2 Next; Thanks to Sprinto and ATOM for Their Support in Reaching This Key Security Milestone",
    "metaDescription": "Hot Aisle completes SOC 2 Type 1 audit, Type 2 coming soon.",
    "metaKeywords": "SOC 2, SOC 2 Type 1, SOC 2 compliance, Hot Aisle, cloud security, Sprinto, ATOM, data protection, audit, information security, compliance audit"
